title: Call This Podcast Pigeon Poop
description: Dave's daughter said something savage to him that he wasn't expecting, someone emails in about seeing Falen do something at a restaurant that they don't agree with, Group Therapy, a guest appearance by Betty Crapper, Dave and Falen try to guess the secret ingredient in Jenny's brownies, War of the Roses, and more!
